snippet.title: Echoes of the Plum Grove - Teaser (Updated)
snippet.description:
A new life calls to you from across the sea… ⛵

Farm, cook, survive, and build a community that will span generations in our brand-new cozy indie game – Echoes of the Plum Grove. Now in development.

Learn more 👉 https://unwoundgames.com/
Follow us on Twitter, Facebook & Instagram 🐦 @UnwoundGames
Wishlist on Steam 📜 https://store.steampowered.com/app/1536090/Echoes_of_the_Plum_Grove/
